sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as API
    participant Auth as AuthManager
    participant Storage as StorageManager
    participant Billing as BillingManager
    participant Obs as ObservabilityManager
    participant AWS as AWS Services
    participant Stripe as Stripe

    FE->>API: POST /auth/login (email, password)
    API->>Auth: login(email, password)
    Auth-->>API: JWT token
    API-->>FE: JWT token

    FE->>API: GET /storage/presigned-url (filename)
    API->>Storage: generate_presigned_url(user_id, filename)
    Storage->>AWS: Request presigned S3 URL
    AWS-->>Storage: Presigned URL
    Storage-->>API: Presigned URL
    API-->>FE: Presigned URL

    FE->>AWS: PUT file to S3 using presigned URL
    AWS-->>FE: Upload success
    FE->>API: POST /billing/usage (usage data)
    API->>Billing: meter_usage(user_id, usage)
    Billing->>Stripe: Record usage
    Stripe-->>Billing: Confirmation
    Billing-->>API: Success
    API-->>FE: Success

    API->>Obs: log_event(event)
    Obs->>AWS: Send logs/metrics to CloudWatch
    Obs->>Sentry: Track error (if any)

    FE->>API: GET /docs
    API-->>FE: OpenAPI docs
